We used an RNA-Seq database generated from purified representative cell type populations in order to generate rank lists of cell type-specific genes [20]. We created seven cell type-specific enrichment rank lists, one for each of the seven representative cell types in the database. Enrichment scores for each cell type were calculated for every gene. These scores E were calculated for each gene i in each cell type j and were computed from their cell type-specific RNA expression levels FPKMij using the following equation:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
